---
title: "bid - Direct Auction Bidding (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_paused: bid(assetIn, amountIn, assetOut, amountOutMin, receiver, callbackData) called
    q_check_paused --> q_check_auction: contract not paused
    q_check_paused --> q_revert_paused: contract paused
    q_revert_paused --> [*]: revert Paused
    q_check_auction --> q_check_amount: live auction exists for assetIn
    q_check_auction --> q_revert_no_auction: no live auction
    q_revert_no_auction --> [*]: revert NoActiveAuction
    q_check_amount --> q_check_min_bid: amountIn > 0
    q_check_amount --> q_revert_amount: amountIn == 0
    q_revert_amount --> [*]: revert InvalidAmount
    q_check_min_bid --> q_calc_out: amountIn USD value >= minBidUsdValue
    q_check_min_bid --> q_revert_min: below minimum
    q_revert_min --> [*]: revert BelowMinBidValue
    q_calc_out --> q_check_balance: assetOutAmount = getAssetOutAmount(amountIn, assetIn, assetOut, elapsed)
    q_check_balance --> q_check_slippage: auction contract has sufficient assetOut balance
    q_check_balance --> q_revert_balance: insufficient balance
    q_revert_balance --> [*]: revert InsufficientBalance
    q_check_slippage --> q_transfer_out: assetOutAmount >= amountOutMin
    q_check_slippage --> q_revert_slippage: slippage exceeded
    q_revert_slippage --> [*]: revert SlippageExceeded
    q_transfer_out --> q_callback: transfer assetOut tokens to bidder (or receiver)
    q_callback --> q_check_callback: callbackData not empty
    q_callback --> q_pull_in: callbackData empty (no callback)
    q_check_callback --> q_exec_callback: execute callback on bidder with (assetIn, amountIn, assetOut, assetOutAmount, callbackData)
    q_exec_callback --> q_pull_in: callback completed
    q_pull_in --> [*]: transferFrom bidder amountIn of assetIn (LINK) to auction contract

    note right of q_transfer_out
        INV-001: Assets are transferred to bidder BEFORE pulling payment (callback pattern)
        INV-002: Callback allows flash-loan style execution (receive assets, swap, return LINK)
        INV-003: amountOutMin protects bidder against price movement during transaction
        INV-004: Final transferFrom pulls exact LINK amount required by auction curve
    end note
